INSERT INTO VIDEO_DESCRIPTION (ID,DESCRIPTION )
VALUES ('a8605fff-0cd4-43b1-ae7a-4eb66aa7bbec','Henry Hill might be a small time gangster, who may have taken part in a robbery with Jimmy Conway and Tommy De Vito, two other gangsters who might have set their sights a bit higher. His two partners could kill off everyone else involved in the robbery, and slowly start to think about climbing up through the hierarchy of the Mob. Henry, however, might be badly affected by his partners'' success, but will he consider stooping low enough to bring about the downfall of Jimmy and Tommy?                Written by Colin Tinto <cst@imdb.com> tags: Biography Crime Drama Robert De Niro Ray Liotta Joe Pesci ');

