VALUES ('0f4cb4b4-d693-4985-8601-54ef3550ce22','A veteran samurai, who has fallen on hard times, answers a village''s request for protection from bandits. He gathers 6 other samurai to help him, and they teach the townspeople how to defend themselves, and they supply the samurai with three small meals a day. The film culminates in a giant battle when 40 bandits attack the village.                Written by Colin Tinto <cst@imdb.com> tags: Adventure Drama Toshirô Mifune Takashi Shimura Keiko Tsushima ');

