INSERT INTO VIDEO_DESCRIPTION (ID,DESCRIPTION )
VALUES ('9f44e23b-a507-4107-937f-23d328eab83d','John Merrick (whose real name was Joseph, as this is based on a true story) is an intelligent and friendly man, but he is hated by his Victorian-era English society because he is severely deformed. Once he is discovered by a doctor, however, he is saved from his life in a freak show and he is treated like the human being that he really is.                Written by Sam Cibula tags: Biography Drama Anthony Hopkins John Hurt Anne Bancroft ');

