INSERT INTO VIDEO_DESCRIPTION (ID,DESCRIPTION )
VALUES ('24df49db-68f6-4beb-82d7-f5d6474be059','Tells the story of Evey Hammond and her unlikely but instrumental part in bringing down the fascist government that has taken control of a futuristic Great Britain. Saved from a life-and-death situation by a man in a Guy Fawkes mask who calls himself V, she learns a general summary of V''s past and, after a time, decides to help him bring down those who committed the atrocities that led to Britain being in the shape that it is in.                Written by ameelmore tags: Action Drama Thriller Hugo Weaving Natalie Portman Rupert Graves ');

