INSERT INTO VIDEO_DESCRIPTION (ID,DESCRIPTION )
VALUES ('35ce6001-3afe-4f72-9dbc-92a5de0449a7','A man calls up the Mumbai police, and tells them he has placed five different bombs in the city -- all set to go off in some time. He wants four terrorists in exchange. Does he get them? Who is behind it all? What''s his motive? Is there more than meets the eye?                Written by Saurabh Roy tags: Crime Drama Mystery Anupam Kher Naseeruddin Shah Jimmy Shergill ');

