VALUES ('6ebd86d2-c9a3-4661-9027-42044ac4f46d','In Bedridge, Professor Parker Wilson finds an abandoned dog at the train station and takes it home with the intention of returning the animal to its owner. He finds that the dog is an Akita and names it Hachiko. However, nobody claims the dog so his family decides to keep Hachi.                Written by Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil tags: Drama Family Richard Gere Joan Allen Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa ');

